    <h2>Download</h2>
    <p>You can download the source code <%= link_to 'here', 'PPMC_src_v0.1.zip'  %>. For now, it has only been tested on Linux 64 bits.</p>
    <p>Instructions about the compilation and the usage are in the README file of the source archive.</p>
